data.description: Solar Owned!! Less than 15 min. drive to Raytheon & shopping. Many custom upgrades in this must see well cared for home in the much sought after Vail School Dist. Level paver driveway with 5400 sqft total throughout property. Extended covered patio with solar screen. Majestic 360 mountain views on corner lot w/no one behind you. Full RV hookup with plenty of space for any length. Rhino Shield exterior paint with 25-year warranty. Bocce Ball court in this meticulously maintained backyard with your very own mini desert botanical garden. All plants on a drip system including fruit trees, 8 saguaros and many rare cacti. Beautiful 8' arched wrought iron front door. Whole home water filtration system, hot water on demand & reverse osmosis in kitchen, and tankless water heater. 30' flagpole from the 1984 Summer Olympics that was given by Frank Borman (Astronaut). Oversized front bedroom. Custom large laundry room. Gas hookup outside with firepit and grill. All tile except 2 rooms. Plus a large den/office with double doors. All appliances included.
